class.rdfs:comment: Indicates a range of postalcodes, usually defined as the set of valid codes between [[postalCodeBegin]] and [[postalCodeEnd]], inclusively.
class.rdfs:label: PostalCodeRangeSpecification

schema:postalCodeBegin.rdfs:comment: First postal code in a range (included).
schema:postalCodeBegin.rdfs:label: postalCodeBegin

schema:postalCodeEnd.rdfs:comment: Last postal code in the range (included). Needs to be after [[postalCodeBegin]].
schema:postalCodeEnd.rdfs:label: postalCodeEnd
